claim.claim-text:
7. A portable computer comprising:
a base part;
pivoting part pivotally coupled to the base part;
a single support structure having first and second leg parts, a middle part separate from the pivoting part connecting the first and second leg parts, and movably projecting from rear portions of the base part, so as to provide support for a pivoting of the pivoting part; and
limiting means for limiting a movement of the first and second leg parts toward or away from the rear portions of the base part at certain distance intervals.
